{"tid":1046204,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"黃士心父子離任 康泰旅行社全面易手海航","createTime":"2019-03-04T05:12:23.000Z","updateTime":"2019-03-04T07:40:57.000Z","uid":6604,"like":15,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":24,"replies":[{"pid":"cb38699be717ab32f4e37431dc602ace74dd6654","tid":1046204,"uid":6604,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:12:23.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190304/59327718\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F59327718&d=i31y%2FnPqUiKwTWzPt1MI4HKg77Sy3LnB9Oyli8DN%2Bms%3D&h=5307327d\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.finance.appledaily.com%2Ffinance%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20190304%2F59327718&h=fac624cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.finance.appledaily.com/finance/realtime/article/20190304/59327718</a><br />\n<br />\n《明報》報道，去年香港航空多名董事「跳船」，令母公司海航內部派系「大洗牌」事件逐漸浮上水面。2011年將51%控股權轉讓予海航背景「勝投國際」的康泰旅行社，其董事長、一直仍持有49%股權的黃士心及其子黃進達，兩人上月已辭任董事並撤出公司，轉由勝投全面接手。  <br />\n<br />\n 公司註冊處資料顯示，黃士心及黃進達父子於上月14日辭任康泰旅行社董事。二人在辭離董事會前，一直持有公司約49%股份，其餘則由與海航有關係的勝投國際投資有限公司持有。"},{"pid":"943e24658b7961fbfaf20e87cc19df97a1559c68","tid":1046204,"uid":79563,"like":31,"dislike":0,"score":31,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:13:40.000Z","msg":"旅行社都好難做啦<br />\n<br />\n賣個好價, 做其他好過"},{"pid":"63f5b8a213b6be4c9c540bea2b0e61f4ac5f0057","tid":1046204,"uid":54373,"like":0,"dislike":5,"score":-5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:14:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> join過佢親自帶隊的美食團"},{"pid":"413f72a608af51756fbf1c6d68e6d6b45a565c04","tid":1046204,"uid":33099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:14:53.000Z","msg":"自己個仔都賣埋"},{"pid":"c450d1331d647c7328ed0fc4333373378851c8c0","tid":1046204,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-03-04T05:15:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/bye.gif\